---
// About Component
---

<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <span class="title-number">01.</span>
        About Me
      </h2>
      <div class="title-underline"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- About Content -->
    <div class="about-content">
      <!-- Main Content Grid -->
      <div class="content-grid">
        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div class="about-text">
          <div class="text-content">
            <p class="intro-text">
              Hello! I'm Andrés Posada, a software engineer with 7 years of
              experience in web and mobile development, specializing in
              JavaScript, Node.js, React, Vue and SQL. I have participated in
              projects from conception to production deployment, designing APIs,
              databases, real-time applications and modernizing critical
              platforms.
            </p>

            <p>
              Throughout my career, I've had the privilege of working across
              diverse sectors including
              <a href="#" class="highlight-link">healthcare</a>,
              <a href="#" class="highlight-link">financial services</a>, and
              <a href="#" class="highlight-link">airport management</a>. My
              expertise spans from building scalable backend architectures to
              crafting intuitive user interfaces, with a strong focus on
              real-time applications and system modernization.
            </p>

            <p>
              I'm passionate about creating robust, efficient solutions that
              solve real-world problems. Whether it's developing instant
              messaging platforms, payment systems, or healthcare management
              software, I bring a comprehensive approach that covers the entire
              development lifecycle.
            </p>

            <p class="technologies-intro">
              Here are the key technologies I work with:
            </p>

            <!-- Technologies List -->
            <div class="technologies-grid">
              <ul class="tech-list">
                <li class="tech-item">JavaScript (ES6+)</li>
                <li class="tech-item">Node.js</li>
                <li class="tech-item">React / React Native</li>
                <li class="tech-item">Vue.js</li>
              </ul>
              <ul class="tech-list">
                <li class="tech-item">PostgreSQL / SQL Server</li>
                <li class="tech-item">Socket.io</li>
                <li class="tech-item">Fastify / NestJS</li>
                <li class="tech-item">MySQL</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Image Side -->
        <div class="about-image">
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <div class="image-overlay"></div>
            <img
              src="/hero-image.jpg"
              alt="Andrés Posada working"
              class="profile-image"
            />
            <div class="image-border"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Experience Timeline -->
      <div class="experience-timeline">
        <h3 class="timeline-title">Professional Experience</h3>

        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-date">2024 - Present</div>
              <h4 class="timeline-job">Software Engineer</h4>
              <p class="timeline-company">Momenge</p>
              <p class="timeline-description">
                Developing an instant messaging application using Fastify,
                PostgreSQL, React Native and Socket.io. Implementing real-time
                event logic, multimedia handling, and account recovery systems.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-date">2021 - 2024</div>
              <h4 class="timeline-job">Full Stack Developer</h4>
              <p class="timeline-company">WeAre Dev</p>
              <p class="timeline-description">
                Designed and developed a remittance platform from scratch using
                Node.js, React, and PostgreSQL. Led migration of legacy systems
                for online payments and loan management, modernizing critical
                financial infrastructure.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-date">2020 - 2021</div>
              <h4 class="timeline-job">Full Stack Developer</h4>
              <p class="timeline-company">O.S Group</p>
              <p class="timeline-description">
                Built a comprehensive platform for credit management and payment
                processing using NestJS and Vue.js. Focused on creating secure,
                scalable financial solutions with robust user interfaces.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-date">2019 - 2020</div>
              <h4 class="timeline-job">Web & Mobile Developer</h4>
              <p class="timeline-company">PLM Group</p>
              <p class="timeline-description">
                Developed web and mobile applications for El Dorado Airport's
                official website. Integrated services for users, flights, and
                COVID surveys, handling high-traffic airport operations.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-date">2018 - 2019</div>
              <h4 class="timeline-job">Lead Software Developer</h4>
              <p class="timeline-company">Sumimedical</p>
              <p class="timeline-description">
                Led development of comprehensive healthcare software with
                patient management, inventory control, real-time chat, and
                multi-database integration (SQL Server, PostgreSQL, MySQL).
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 4rem 0 6rem 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .container {
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1250px;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  /* Section Header */
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .title-number {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff 0%, #9c40ff 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .title-underline {
    width: 100px;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff 0%, #9c40ff 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  /* Content Grid */
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  /* About Text */
  .about-text {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .highlight-link {
    color: #00d4ff;
    text-decoration: none;
    position: relative;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .highlight-link:hover {
    color: #9c40ff;
  }

  .highlight-link::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    bottom: -2px;
    left: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff 0%, #9c40ff 100%);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .highlight-link:hover::after {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .technologies-intro {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Technologies Grid */
  .technologies-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .tech-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .tech-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .tech-item::before {
    content: "▸";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #00d4ff;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  /* About Image */
  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 280px;
    height: 350px;
  }

  .profile-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    filter: grayscale(20%);
  }

  .image-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2),
      rgba(156, 64, 255, 0.2)
    );
    border-radius: 12px;
    z-index: 3;
    opacity: 0.8;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .image-border {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    left: 20px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 2px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
    border-radius: 12px;
    z-index: 1;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .image-wrapper:hover .profile-image {
    transform: translate(-10px, -10px);
    filter: grayscale(0%);
  }

  .image-wrapper:hover .image-overlay {
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .image-wrapper:hover .image-border {
    transform: translate(10px, 10px);
    border-color: rgba(156, 64, 255, 0.6);
  }

  /* Experience Timeline */
  .experience-timeline {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .timeline-title {
    font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff 0%, #9c40ff 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 1rem;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #00d4ff 0%, #9c40ff 50%, #ff006e 100%);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: -2rem;
    top: 0.5rem;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    background: #00d4ff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .timeline-content {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-content:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
    transform: translateX(10px);
  }

  .timeline-date {
    color: #00d4ff;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-job {
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .timeline-company {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .timeline-description {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .container {
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .image-wrapper {
      width: 320px;
      height: 400px;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .container {
      padding: 0 3rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 5rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
